OL,3,CWhy Coventry City's owner risks fan
OL,4,Cbacklash over sacking Mark Robins
OL,6,FCoventry City sacking manager Mark
OL,7,FRobins is the biggest decision of
OL,8,Fowner Doug King's time at the club.
OL,10,FIt is a bombshell and not without risk.
OL,12,FThe awkwardness will begin this
OL,13,Fweekend in Sunderland when there is an
OL,14,Fexpectation many Sky Blues fans will
OL,15,Fsing the name of their axed boss.
OL,17,FRobins is revered in Coventry for his
OL,18,Fwork over eight years during the
OL,19,Fclub's darkest moments.
