OL,3,CWhy Coventry City's owner risks fan
OL,4,Cbacklash over sacking Mark Robins
OL,6,FThis summer there were sweeping
OL,7,Fchanges to the coaching staff as the
OL,8,Fclub modernised and set itself up to
OL,9,Fhave a 'head coach' rather than a
OL,10,Fmanager who controls almost everything.
OL,12,FThis will be King's first head coach
OL,13,Fappointment and he will want to make a
OL,14,Fstatement.
OL,16,FThe easiest way to do that is with a
OL,17,Fbig name.
OL,19,FIt is sad that Robins won't be the man
OL,20,Fto take Coventry all the way to the
OL,21,FPremier League.
